BC Website Statistics extension FEATURES

FEATURES
============

1. PageView Statistics
   -------------------

This extension provides a template operator and settings which upon installation
will output the requirired javascript into your eZ publish design html output
which sends website visitor statistics per pageview to the Google Analytics
web service.


2. Order Statistics
   ----------------

This extension provides a template operator, workflow event and settings which
upon installation will output the requirired javascript into your eZ publish 
design html output which sends website customer webshop order statistics per
pageview to the Google Analytics web service.


3. Google Analytics Reporting
   --------------------------

The Google Analytics website, http://www.google.com/analytics

This website provides a dynamic flash based web application for viewing your
websites pageview and order statistics collected by the Google Analytics
web service transmited by the BC Google Analyticics extension.


4. eZ Publish Multi-Site Installations now supported
   -------------------------------------------------
